# Potato3D Engine #
**Potato3D Engine** is simple lightweight 3D Engine written in C++0x and OpenGL 4.x. 

## What's done:
+ 	VBO/VAO
+ 	Render to texture/FBO
+ 	Custom matrix stack implementation
+	Matrix math
+ 	Bitmap fonts
+	Specular/Diffuse/Ambient Lighting
+	Materials
+	****.obj/*.mtl*** mesh loading
+	Normal mapping

